<item>
            <title>[KAFKA-5040] Increase number of Streams producer retries from the default of 0</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KAFKA-5040</link>
                <project id="12311720" key="KAFKA">Kafka</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In Kafka Streams, the default value for the producer retries is not changed from the default of 0. That leads to situations where a streams instance fails when a broker is temporarily unavailable. Increasing this number to &amp;gt; 0 would help.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
